    "For instance, an AI-driven system embedded within a VR platform can coordinate multiple sensory cues (Bhowmik 2024).",
    "It may align visual elements, such as the color and presentation of food, with corresponding auditory inputs like sizzling or chopping sounds while also delivering targeted olfactory stimuli that correspond to the virtual meal.",
    "This synchronized multisensory stimulation enhances both realism and immersion.",
    "By aligning visual, auditory, and olfactory cues, the system can guide users through richer and more engaging flavor experiences.",
    "Such integration may help users explore unfamiliar cuisines, increase enjoyment of nutritionally beneficial yet bland foods, and even enable the creation of entirely new culinary experiences that are difficult to achieve in conventional settings."
